    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四妓女",
        "曹老西",
        "老鸨子",
        "陈三两"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身在烟花柳巷，搜罗美貌婵娟。迎接王孙公子，一心只图银钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，老鸨子的便是。在这洛阳城中，开一座九开间门大窑子。前月里买了一个"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，长的倒也不错。只是她不肯修饰打扮，她说要叫她接客，却也不难，见"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她一面，要银三两。自从她进了我的门，还没有开过张呐。看这几天，连阴大"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雨。今天也到晴啦。间壁人家吹弹歌唱，十分热闹。唯独我们这院里冷冷清清，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连一个人影儿也没有。到门口去望望去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹老西上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子流水板",
          "musical_style": "梆子流水板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "急急忙忙往前奔，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子流水板",
          "musical_style": "梆子流水板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "不觉来到了一家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子看曹老西。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我说大爷，您哪怎么老不来啦？昨天我还念诵您来着。走走，家里坐吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你同我亲热的很，你知道我是谁呀？我姓什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你姓赵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不照。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是姓钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钱倒有的是。你看看金子银子通多得很。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你光景是姓孙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要胡猜乱猜。我姓曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，是的。你是曹二爷么！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不对。我弟兄只有一个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吧。家里坐着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我来问问你，你同我乱拉近乎，你是个做什么的人呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这儿就是窑子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈哈！这倒巧啦，我今天正想逛窑子。你是个做什么的人呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我呀，我就这窑子里头的老板。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就是这铺子里头的掌柜呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢，你老人家请进来吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这里是窑子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，我就同你进去坐坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这院里的姑娘都在哪儿藏着？为何不出来呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别忙，待我去叫她们去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说都来见见！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子下。四妓女同上。曹老西看四妓女。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你们哪一个是陈三两呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四妓女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "懂得逛窑子再来逛，什么陈三两，李四两，真是七担不够，八蛋肏得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四妓女同下。曹老西呆。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈！真正欺负我们老西，见了面，可就骂起来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌柜的快来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听一声唤，急忙到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷有什么事呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这窑子真真欺生。见了我，刚说了一句话，她们为何就骂起来我啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她们不敢呐，必是你能说了犯恶的话啦吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就问了她一声：“你们哪一个叫陈三两”，她们就骂起来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪不得，这是你能不在行。待我给你赔个不是吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们这里可有一个陈三两没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈三两，我们这里倒有此人。但是她见客一面，必须要花三两银子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要住她，要多少钱？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子看曹老西包袱。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要是住她也倒容易。我有一件家伙，等我去拿了来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子取斗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来吧，这是我们这里的规矩，要能够把斗用银子填满了，你就住她。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。我有银子，待我取出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹老西解包袱取一锭银子掷斗内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一锭不够。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹老西取一锭银子掷斗内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这可是真满啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早着哪，你别怕花银子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这个斗真是填不满的坑。我全都给你吧，你看看满不满？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就算满了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子转身，曹老西向地上拾。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还有一点银子渣儿呐。待我带起来吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老人家在这儿等一等，待我去叫她出来陪你吃酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对啦。你给我预备好酒，今天我老西是要开开心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈三两蓬头垢面暗上，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的银子是花了，不知道陈三两长得有多好看。今日同她困觉，真真不枉人生"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一世。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹老西转身见陈三两，呆。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家陈三两。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹老西后退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是陈三两？咳，我曹老西真真晦气，陈三两怎么是这样一个人。咳，银子已"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "经花了，管他这些那些，捞捞本钱再说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，猜拳喝酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家鸡不打团团转，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "野鸡不打遥天飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要穿还是粗布衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈三两",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要吃还是家常饭"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要吃还是家常饭"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "听一言来甚惨凄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "两泪交流洒湿衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "不由我想起了自己妻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "她把好言将我劝"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "叫一声掌柜的你快来吧"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷什么事情呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "叫一声掌柜的你听端的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大爷，你放着酒不吃，怎么倒哭起来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哎，我的掌柜的呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "陈三两方才来劝我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "倒叫我心中好惨凄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "要穿还是粗布衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "梆子摇板",
          "musical_style": "梆子摇板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "野鸡不打遥天飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌柜的，快把银子还给我，我老西从今以后，再也不敢逛窑子啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她言道要吃还是家常饭"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家鸡打得团团转"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大爷，你为什么哭起来啦？她说的也是几句好话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我知道她是好话。是你不知道，我从山西出门的时候，我的母亲曾经教训过我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不叫在外边浪荡逍遥。她对我也说过这几句话来。今天陈三两她也对我说这"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几句话，我不由得就想起我的老母亲来啦。今天我这不是来逛窑子来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么你来做什么来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我简直是来听教训来啦。陈三两她竟把我当做她的儿子来教训起来啦吗？掌柜"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "的，你把我的银子快快还了我吧。我老西从今往后，再也不敢逛窑子了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，你能不要伤心啦，我把这酒菜端到我那一间房子里去，请大爷到我房里"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃一杯酒，我来陪你，你看好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你陪我吃酒？好好。看你年纪虽然是大一点儿，倒还风骚得很。没有想到，今"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹老西",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天掌柜的也接起客来啦。走，我尝尝你这个老家伙是个什么滋味。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老鸨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦，别胡说八道，跟着我走吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老鸨子拉曹老西同下。）"
        }
